    "thumbnail": ""
  },
  "source_transcript_segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.64,
      "text": "I tried my best, but I couldn't do anything about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.64,
      "end": 19.04,
      "text": "Tak, you're not the only one who's been fighting in that tiny mountain, are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.04,
      "end": 23.48,
      "text": "By the way, do you know what's happening right now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.48,
      "end": 26.28,
      "text": "You too, Yamayu, are in your head."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.77,
      "end": 27.77,
      "text": "Why do you even turn your head?"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.77,
      "end": 31.77,
      "text": "What's the reason for that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.77,
      "end": 38.77,
      "text": "Why do you want to kill me from now on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.77,
      "end": 45.77,
      "text": "I don't know what you're feeling."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.77,
      "end": 50.77,
      "text": "I can't understand what's going on here."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.38,
      "end": 53.38,
      "text": "What is it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.38,
      "end": 55.38,
      "text": "Wait a minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.38,
      "end": 57.38,
      "text": "What is this guy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.38,
      "end": 65.38,
      "text": "Why do you think I have nothing to say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.38,
      "end": 68.38,
      "text": "I refuse."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.38,
      "end": 71.38,
      "text": "You're not going to open the door."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.38,
      "end": 75.38,
      "text": "I called you at the beginning."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.38,
      "end": 77.38,
      "text": "You've been there for a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.99,
      "end": 77.99,
      "text": "I'll always be there for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.99,
      "end": 80.99,
      "text": "Oh? What are you talking about?"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.99,
      "end": 83.99,
      "text": "Zouken was killed by Onigari!"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.99,
      "end": 89.99,
      "text": "Did Musan-sama ask you for something?"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.99,
      "end": 92.99,
      "text": "Eh?"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.99,
      "end": 95.99,
      "text": "No, but I'm Saitama."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.99,
      "end": 97.99,
      "text": "I'm a hero."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.99,
      "end": 101.99,
      "text": "You fought well, Nagori Oshiiga."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.21,
      "end": 104.71,
      "text": "I'm sorry, but it's time to end this."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.91,
      "end": 106.91,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.11,
      "end": 109.11,
      "text": "It's gone?"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.91,
      "end": 114.21,
      "text": "This guy!"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.71,
      "end": 117.21,
      "text": "Come on, let's do this together!"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.91,
      "end": 124.91,
      "text": "What the..."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.72,
      "end": 126.72,
      "text": "I'm glad I did it."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.72,
      "end": 133.72,
      "text": "What a great time!"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.72,
      "end": 137.72,
      "text": "That's great!"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.72,
      "end": 139.72,
      "text": "Let me have more fun!"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.72,
      "end": 142.72,
      "text": "Are they coming to see me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.72,
      "end": 145.72,
      "text": "I'll keep going!"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.72,
      "end": 148.72,
      "text": "I'm not a one-year-old warrior!"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.26,
      "end": 154.26,
      "text": "You fought well. I'll make a decision."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.26,
      "end": 158.26,
      "text": "I feel like my hand hit something just now."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.26,
      "end": 159.26,
      "text": "Are you okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.26,
      "end": 162.26,
      "text": "I can't understand it at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 164.26,
      "end": 166.26,
      "text": "I'm going to die!"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.26,
      "end": 172.26,
      "text": "Don't overdo it."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.08,
      "end": 178.88,
      "text": "I-I can't believe he's a friend of mine!"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.88,
      "end": 183.08,
      "text": "I've made up my mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.08,
      "end": 185.08,
      "text": "That's great!"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.08,
      "end": 191.08,
      "text": "Hey, do you want to know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.08,
      "end": 198.08,
      "text": "You're going to make me expect a lot of things from you, aren't you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.08,
      "end": 200.08,
      "text": "You bastard."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.99,
      "end": 204.99,
      "text": "Hehehehehehehehehehehehehehe"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.08,
      "end": 207.08,
      "text": "I-I can't believe he's a friend of mine!"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.99,
      "end": 206.99,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.99,
      "end": 208.99,
      "text": "Be on now"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.99,
      "end": 210.99,
      "text": "Eh, Muzan-sama"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.99,
      "end": 214.99,
      "text": "You aren't going to kill him, are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.26,
      "end": 215.26,
      "text": "Why don't you do it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.83,
      "end": 217.83,
      "text": "So you're calling me here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.83,
      "end": 221.83,
      "text": "Kill me!"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.83,
      "end": 223.83,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.83,
      "end": 237.83,
      "text": "Wait a minute, Mr. Akazado."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.83,
      "end": 240.83,
      "text": "Don't you worry about me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.83,
      "end": 243.83,
      "text": "If you hurry, you'll make it!"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.18,
      "end": 244.18,
      "text": "It's time for fun!"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.18,
      "end": 249.18,
      "text": "Finally, it's my turn!"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.18,
      "end": 251.18,
      "text": "Who are you at this time?"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.18,
      "end": 255.18,
      "text": "I was really worried about everyone."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.18,
      "end": 257.18,
      "text": "Because I'm an important friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.18,
      "end": 260.18,
      "text": "I don't want anyone to blame me."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.18,
      "end": 262.18,
      "text": "Mr. Akazado?"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.18,
      "end": 265.18,
      "text": "I was beaten by an onigiri."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.18,
      "end": 266.18,
      "text": "What are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.18,
      "end": 268.18,
      "text": "At that time, I was hit by an onigiri."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.18,
      "end": 271.18,
      "text": "Because he is a master of martial arts."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.57,
      "end": 273.57,
      "text": "I'm not saying it's his fault, but I'm just interested in it."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.57,
      "end": 277.57,
      "text": "I'm not saying it's for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.57,
      "end": 280.57,
      "text": "I'm just a woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.57,
      "end": 282.57,
      "text": "Listen to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.57,
      "end": 288.57,
      "text": "Akas, you are hiding your appearance from the public."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.96,
      "end": 294.96,
      "text": "You can't even see the curse."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.96,
      "end": 296.96,
      "text": "Both of them are fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.96,
      "end": 300.96,
      "text": "There is no power left to shake the sword many times."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.96,
      "end": 302.96,
      "text": "What are you doing all of a sudden?"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.96,
      "end": 307.96,
      "text": "My sword is not for you to cut your hair."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.96,
      "end": 309.96,
      "text": "Oh, it's broken."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.96,
      "end": 312.96,
      "text": "What? Is this an old man?"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.96,
      "end": 313.96,
      "text": "I won't let you do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.96,
      "end": 314.96,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.96,
      "end": 315.96,
      "text": "Shut up."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.96,
      "end": 317.96,
      "text": "I won't let you do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.96,
      "end": 318.96,
      "text": "I won't let you do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.96,
      "end": 319.96,
      "text": "I won't let you do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.29,
      "end": 319.79,
      "text": "Eh?"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.79,
      "end": 320.79,
      "text": "Shut up."
    },
    {
      "start": 319.96,
      "end": 320.96,
      "text": "I won't let you do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.79,
      "end": 323.49,
      "text": "Oh, it's a shield?"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.49,
      "end": 326.29,
      "text": "That means this bomb is really strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.79,
      "end": 330.79,
      "text": "Wasn't it a new weapon?"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.79,
      "end": 332.09,
      "text": "Then what was it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.09,
      "end": 333.09,
      "text": "It was just a cut."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.09,
      "end": 335.59,
      "text": "I knew it from the start."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.59,
      "end": 338.79,
      "text": "I hope you can eat your own strategy."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.49,
      "end": 342.49,
      "text": "If you don't do it like that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.49,
      "end": 344.49,
      "text": "it's going to be a lot of trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.99,
      "end": 348.49,
      "text": "The AQ-1 is aiming at the new weapon."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.0,
      "end": 349.3,
      "text": "and the AQ-1 will come out."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.3,
      "end": 353.5,
      "text": "You scoundrel."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.0,
      "end": 357.3,
      "text": "Well, I have a conclusion now, but..."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.3,
      "end": 359.0,
      "text": "I refuse."
    },
    {
      "start": 359.3,
      "end": 361.3,
      "text": "Hey, so let's eat meat."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.8,
      "end": 366.8,
      "text": "Lord Jogen called me first."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.2,
      "end": 369.7,
      "text": "Do you want to know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.7,
      "end": 371.6,
      "text": "Are you the final weapon here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.6,
      "end": 373.8,
      "text": "It's obviously different from the ones in the police."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.75,
      "end": 377.75,
      "text": "I hate weak people."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.8,
      "end": 375.6,
      "text": "I am..."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.75,
      "end": 381.75,
      "text": "No matter how hard I try, I can't defeat a demon."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.75,
      "end": 383.75,
      "text": "Really? That's what I'm talking about."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.75,
      "end": 387.75,
      "text": "I don't remember anything about the person who hit me."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.75,
      "end": 389.75,
      "text": "What do you think? You're having fun, aren't you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.75,
      "end": 391.75,
      "text": "Let's fight more!"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.75,
      "end": 394.75,
      "text": "Let's have more fun!"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.75,
      "end": 396.75,
      "text": "Become a demon!"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.75,
      "end": 398.75,
      "text": "I hate weak people too."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.75,
      "end": 402.75,
      "text": "If that's the case, even in 100 years, even in 200 years..."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.89,
      "end": 403.89,
      "text": "Even in the last 100 years, even in the last 200 years, I will continue to train."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.89,
      "end": 405.89,
      "text": "I will definitely do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.89,
      "end": 407.89,
      "text": "Your strength..."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.89,
      "end": 410.89,
      "text": "It's been a long time since I joined the Hero Association."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.89,
      "end": 413.89,
      "text": "I was interested in Hero Street for a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.89,
      "end": 416.89,
      "text": "That's why I came to the fighting game."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.89,
      "end": 422.89,
      "text": "Even if you become a demon, you can't continue to fight without caring about your wounds."
    },
    {
      "start": 423.89,
      "end": 429.89,
      "text": "The people who don't have Mobishiro can't enjoy their growth anymore."
    },
    {
      "start": 428.21,
      "end": 430.21,
      "text": "I can't do it anymore."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.21,
      "end": 433.21,
      "text": "No matter how many monsters I deal with,"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.21,
      "end": 437.21,
      "text": "I can't do anything about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.21,
      "end": 440.21,
      "text": "Heroes are such lonely creatures."
    },
    {
      "start": 441.21,
      "end": 443.21,
      "text": "I'll become stronger."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.21,
      "end": 446.21,
      "text": "I'll become even stronger!"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.21,
      "end": 449.21,
      "text": "Existence, development, escape!"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.21,
      "end": 454.21,
      "text": "It's a wonderful moment!"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.31,
      "end": 455.31,
      "text": "It's a wonderful moment!"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.31,
      "end": 457.31,
      "text": "Hahahahaha!"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.31,
      "end": 459.31,
      "text": "While chasing the scars of that thing,"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.31,
      "end": 461.31,
      "text": "that spirit, that spirit power!"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.31,
      "end": 463.31,
      "text": "Now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.31,
      "end": 465.31,
      "text": "it's time for the end."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.31,
      "end": 467.31,
      "text": "Did it disappear?"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.31,
      "end": 469.31,
      "text": "Kill me!"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.31,
      "end": 471.31,
      "text": "Get off me!"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.31,
      "end": 473.31,
      "text": "You're in the way!"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.31,
      "end": 475.31,
      "text": "What are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.31,
      "end": 476.31,
      "text": "Hey."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.31,
      "end": 478.31,
      "text": "It's fine! I did it well!"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.31,
      "end": 481.31,
      "text": "Ah, it's closed."
    },
    {
      "start": 481.05,
      "end": 483.05,
      "text": "Ah, I'm screwed."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.05,
      "end": 486.05,
      "text": "Idiot!"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.05,
      "end": 488.05,
      "text": "What are you doing? Hey!"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.05,
      "end": 489.05,
      "text": "You bastard!"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.05,
      "end": 495.05,
      "text": "I've never seen a person without a weapon like you in the last few hundred years."
    },
    {
      "start": 496.05,
      "end": 499.05,
      "text": "I had a weapon that was as thin as a baby."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.98,
      "end": 507.98,
      "text": "Show me your power!"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.05,
      "end": 506.05,
      "text": "Let me see!"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.98,
      "end": 510.98,
      "text": "Your body will never be able to withstand it!"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.98,
      "end": 511.98,
      "text": "Ugatsu!"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.98,
      "end": 513.98,
      "text": "With your full power, Ugatsu!"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.98,
      "end": 516.98,
      "text": "If you don't become stronger than anyone else,"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.98,
      "end": 517.98,
      "text": "I'm going to die!"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.98,
      "end": 519.98,
      "text": "You don't understand well."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.98,
      "end": 521.98,
      "text": "You have a lot of chance."
    },
    {
      "start": 521.98,
      "end": 522.98,
      "text": "Maybe Otaku?"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.98,
      "end": 524.98,
      "text": "I've made up my mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.98,
      "end": 527.98,
      "text": "No problem."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.98,
      "end": 528.98,
      "text": "No matter what kind of attack it is,"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.98,
      "end": 531.98,
      "text": "I will not let you destroy my body!"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.99,
      "end": 531.99,
      "text": "I can feel the evil spirit!"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.99,
      "end": 534.99,
      "text": "The evil spirit's reaction is also strong!"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.99,
      "end": 536.99,
      "text": "I'm going to hit you."
    },
    {
      "start": 538.99,
      "end": 539.99,
      "text": "Idiot!"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.99,
      "end": 541.99,
      "text": "The time has disappeared!"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.99,
      "end": 543.99,
      "text": "There's no time!"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.99,
      "end": 544.99,
      "text": "Calm down!"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.49,
      "end": 559.49,
      "text": "You're a fool. Don't make me mad."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.49,
      "end": 564.49,
      "text": "You didn't want to be strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.49,
      "end": 568.49,
      "text": "Did you think this is the end?"
    },
    {
      "start": 571.49,
      "end": 573.49,
      "text": "What? Mr. Akaza..."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.49,
      "end": 576.49,
      "text": "Did he die?"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.49,
      "end": 578.49,
      "text": "He died, so..."
    },
